POE-SAPI version 0.01
=====================

POE::SAPI is a simple API based in POE that allows a user to quickly develop 
efficiant, cross platform network utilities and tools.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	Bundle::POE
	
	

